reviewText: Did not receive the movies advertised.
The worse package I have ever received .Outside was ripped. Jewel cases were in pieces. The few times it played the picture was horrible. I don't  think any part of this was new.

Some interesting movies in the early part of these actresses careers... Worthy to see at least one time. Didn't really care for Killer Cruise & the video quality of the movies is not too good & even a bit blurry if you watch on a large flat screen.

The listing was for six movies, but only one dvd (with two movies on it) was sent. I was VERY disappointed, as I had ordered it specifically for one of the missing movies which is almost impossible to find. I haven't been able to continue the seller, so I thought I would warn any future buyers to beware!
